text:
This is one place i really admire.. We all have problems and they can change every week, every day every month or a minute...
. But i feel so blessed that everytime i attended the church i had answers to my thoughts... I feel as if someone is listening to me and taking care of everything that I am going through...
Awesome worship, preaching & spiritual family experience !
Hope to visit EN Singapore someday
The worship atmosphere is gracious, it is close to HarbourFront Station and has good accessibility, and English worship is held every Sunday at 11 o'clock.
